### Get All Transfers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Transfer
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Internal Transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/internal
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 100.00,
  "description": "Transfer to savings"
}

### External Transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/external
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountNumber": "1234567890",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "recipientName": "John Doe",
  "description": "Payment for services"
}

### Verify Account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/verify-account
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountNumber": "1234567890"
}

### Scheduled Transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/scheduled
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 100.00,
  "scheduledDate": "2023-12-31",
  "description": "Scheduled transfer"
}

### Get Scheduled Transfers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/scheduled?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Cancel Transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Recurring Transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/recurring
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 100.00,
  "frequency": "MONTHLY",
  "startDate": "2023-01-01",
  "endDate": "2023-12-31",
  "description": "Monthly savings"
}

### Get Recurring Transfers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/recurring?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Cancel Recurring Transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/recurring/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Transfer Receipt
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/1/receipt
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Pending Transfers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/pending?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Transfer Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/statistics
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Transfer Limits
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/limits
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transfers/health
